or之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a9a8af6771ba728e1d7e0d66467fd25fd2c2a6","tid":111672,"uid":70829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:25:42.000Z","msg":"西班牙必去Barcelona, Sevilla, Granada, Valencia<br />\nMadrid其實唔太值得去<br />\nMalaga唯一賣點係Picasso museum,但如果你會去Barcelona個Picasso museum，可以唔洗去Malaga <br />\n有時間的話，Ronda都去得過"},{"pid":"95bb12b9b60f30ecbeec438f886fa79af24c34b8","tid":111672,"uid":23399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:34:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>前兩年去左十幾日克羅地亞, 我就自駕既, 不過唔自駕搭巴士都幾方便</blockquote><br />\n應該預幾多日留係croatia呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實好睇你點玩, 克羅地亞個海好靚, 你summer去就更加要留D時間去玩水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己玩得好hea, 例如留左3日係hvar個島上面望下海, 參加tour出海去blue cave之類<br />\n正常咁玩, 上面巴打suggest個行程我估大概10日都夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ndubrovnik可以再join tour去kotor之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我好鍾意睇海玩水 唔該哂你巴打 ！ 治安係咪都好？ 多唔多人比人偷野"},{"pid":"398c59ad140c26d71b3422685caec1b9201160f9","tid":111672,"uid":23399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:35:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西班牙必去Barcelona, Sevilla, Granada, Valencia<br />\nMadrid其實唔太值得去<br />\nMalaga唯一賣點係Picasso museum,但如果你會去Barcelona個Picasso museum，可以唔洗去Malaga <br />\n有時間的話，Ronda都去得過</blockquote><br />\n我其實去過Barcelona + Madrid 幾鍾意巴塞 馬德里好悶<br />\n唔該哂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2cb4069ddf55843e85a219ee027b417c78f7a2","tid":111672,"uid":80580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T11:46:19.000Z","msg":"克羅地亞好正"},{"pid":"0af8652fc54e88568ebb61ae375c4f2d062faf70","